beer.beer_description:
Time has come to delve into the sub-terrane of wastelands. The pinnacle of civilisation once stood here, breathtakingly ignorant in its splendour. Beg not for succour, but heed the turgid monstrosities of malign intent.

A new world Red Rye Ale, where caramel, biscuit and spicey malts match new and classic hop varieties. The earthy rye character provides the stage for grass, pine and lemon hop notes, finishing in a smooth bitterness.
